docs.text: PythaiNAV ¶ ทำให้การดึงข้อมูล กองทุนไทย เป็นเรื่องง่าย Get Started - เริ่มต้นใช้งาน ¶ ติดตั้ง PythaiNAV ก่อน 1 pip install pythainav 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 >>> import pythainav as nav >>> nav . get ( "KT-PRECIOUS" ) Nav ( value = 4.2696 , updated = '20/01/2020' , tags = { 'latest' }, fund = 'KT-PRECIOUS' ) >>> nav . get ( "TISTECH-A" ) Nav ( value = 12.9976 , updated = '21/01/2020' , tags = { 'latest' }, fund = 'TISTECH-A' )

docs.text: API Reference - อ้างอิง API ¶ pythainav. get ( fund_name , source='finnomena' , **kargs ) Gets the latest NAV Parameters: fund_name - Fund name found in finnomena such as TISTECH-A source - (optional) Data source for pull data. See Data Sources section in the documentation for all availiable options. subscription_key - (optional) Subscription key that required for a data source like sec (a.k.a) Returns: Nav Usage: 1 2 3 4 >>> import pythainav as nav >>> nav . get ( "KT-PRECIOUS" ) Nav ( value = 4.2696 , updated = '20/01/2020' , tags = { 'latest' }, fund = 'KT-PRECIOUS' )
docs.title: API Reference
